{"tid":2019741,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"2019年理大圍城的士司機接載FA時受傷","createTime":"2020-05-16T13:27:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T14:28:47.000Z","uid":352010,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"898c551f05e81ea6fa87747c7c16279fafacbc34","tid":2019741,"uid":352010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T13:27:55.000Z","msg":"本人於<strong>2019年11月18日約上午5:20在紅磡機利士南路與曲街交界處</strong>，駕駛的士接載一名年約25歲男性FA前往將軍澳時，因有需要而要下車時<strong>被相信來自催淚鎗的强大氣流沖至整個人仆低，左肩脫較。</strong>由於公司要求，本人便在上述乘客的急救及照顧下用慢速駛回將軍澳交更地。本人其後入急症室治療，至今尚未康復，左手只有約六成活動能力。本人現考慮對有關當局索償，急請以上乘客透過范國威議員電郵garyfantko@gmail.com 或直接電郵lcnpeterng@yahoo.com.hk與本人聯絡。謝謝。"},{"pid":"cdd6b696a9e3a707e2632a4ce70db20cd4dbe88b","tid":2019741,"uid":224249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T13:30:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"04f9c806de82b819b4b2d4512aadad52aefbd44b","tid":2019741,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T13:30:35.000Z","msg":"你真係好鬼。。。唔知信唔信你好<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e3kEs6o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe3kEs6o.png&h=2daf941c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"02c397839632d132f4099b4ae9c3e30f63253f06","tid":2019741,"uid":165654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T13:30:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3c2a6e44d2ecd662ecad78bc40cad78168afc90c","tid":2019741,"uid":197939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T14:11:26.000Z","msg":"推比民陣睇！想反國歌法嘅入尼！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2019775\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2019775</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"976d9f04eb627c069f0ea3fd1eb178a382d9f30b","tid":2019741,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T14:28:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n除非范國威出賣手足，否則應該冇野"}]}